text: Tullinge torg is a small shopping center in Botkyrka located in central Tullinge, Sweden. Nearby is Tullinge station. Tullinge Torg has over 20 shops including a pizza vendor and a solarium. == History == Tullinge Torg was built in the 1970s. Category:Shopping centres in Sweden Category:Stockholm urban area
